T02TD2112E:153b-0: @153b ` // bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2112E:153b-2: sprul sku lam du byed pa rdo rje'i glu ni /
T02TD2112E:153b-3: aom badzra t'ikshna rdo rje rnon po bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas so //
T02TD2112E:153b-4: du:kha tstshe dmi mthun pa'i sdug bsngal gcod pa mi bskyod pa'o //
T02TD2112E:153b-6: shes rab ye shes gti mug sel ba rnam snang ngo //
T02TD2112E:153b-8: ye shes kyi sku phrin las byed pa don yod grub pa'o //
T02TD2112E:153b-9: w'a g'i shva ra ngag gi dbang phyug gdul bya tshim pa /
T02TD2112E:153b-10: aa ra pa tsa ma skyes pa'i don rin chen 'byung ldan /
T02TD2112E:153b-11: aom te te h'um bde ba'i don rtogs /
T02TD2112E:153b-12: te na h'um bde ba'i lam rnyed /
T02TD2112E:153b-13: te te te na h'um gnyis su med pa'i bde ba thob pa'o //
T02TD2112E:153b-14: ya te na ma:theg chen ma nor ba yin no //
T02TD2112E:153b-15: bar du dge ba'i don ni /
T02TD2112E:153b-16: longs sku lam du byed pa rdo rje'i glu ni /
T02TD2112E:153b-17: aom sthi to hri di chos thams cad rang bzhin skye med kyi ngo bor gnas /
T02TD2112E:153b-19: ye shes kyi bde ba rang la yod /
T02TD2112E:153b-21: sangs rgyas sems can ye nas gnyis su med /
T02TD2112E:153b-23: dus gsum gyi don brjod pa las 'das pa'i gnas yin /
T02TD2112E:153b-27: te te te na h'um thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i bde ba thob po //
T02TD2112E:153b-28: mthar thug dag pa'i don ni /
T02TD2112E:153b-29: chos sku lam du byed pa rdo rje'i glu ni /
T02TD2112E:153b-31: chos thams cad skye ba med pa nyid /
T02TD2112E:153b-34: skye med skye ba med pa nyid du snang /
T02TD2112E:153b-36: ma skyes chos rnams dus gsum yid kyis dran /
T02TD2112E:153b-38: chos rnams skye med mi 'da' dam tshig nyid //
T02TD2112E:154a-0: chos rnams thams cad longs spyod mchog / aom sarba dharm'a @154a * //
T02TD2112E:154a-2: chos thams cad 'bras bu bde ba che /
T02TD2112E:154a-3: aom sarba dharm'a aa:chos sku bde ba chen po nyid kyi don /
T02TD2112E:154a-4: aom te te h'um bde ba'i don rtogs /
T02TD2112E:154a-5: te na h'um bde ba'i lam rnyed /
T02TD2112E:154a-6: te te te na h'um gnyis su med pa'i bde ba thob /
T02TD2112E:154a-7: ya te na ma:theg pa chen po ma nor ba yin glu dang po bum dbang thob bas blang //
T02TD2112E:154a-8: glu bar pa de gsang dbang dang /
T02TD2112E:154a-9: shes rab ye shes thob pas blang /
T02TD2112E:154a-10: glu gsum pa de dbang bzhi thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa chen pos blang ngo //
T02TD2112E:154a-11: rdo rje glu'i gdams ngag rdzogs so//
